data.title: Domesticated Plants
data.meta_description: 1591610281 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides a guide to poisonous house and garden plants. It lists over 400 plant species grouped alphabetically from A-Z with their common names. For many of the plants, the document describes their primary toxins and clinical effects. Tables are included that group plants according to their primary toxins such as alkaloids, glycosides, and saponins. Another table lists plants and their general clinical effects such as vomiting, diarrhea, and respiratory failure.
